OL,3,CTrain passengers warned of 'major
OL,4,Cdisruption' for rest of day amid radio
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,FTrain services across southern England
OL,8,Fare being disrupted by a fault with a
OL,9,Fradio system.
OL,11,FNational Rail Enquiries said the issue
OL,12,Frelates to how train drivers and
OL,13,Fsignallers communicate.
OL,15,FIt warned passengers that services may
OL,16,Fbe delayed by up to 45 minutes or
OL,17,Fcancelled, and "major disruption is
OL,18,Fexpected until the end of the day".
OL,26,@yD@POUzD@bO]
