OL,3,CTrain passengers warned of 'major
OL,4,Cdisruption' for rest of day amid radio
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,FThe affected operators are
OL,8,FCrossCountry, Gatwick Express, Great
OL,9,FWestern Railway, London Overground,
OL,10,FSouthern, South Western Railway (SWR)
OL,11,Fand Thameslink.
OL,13,FThe incident was reported shortly
OL,14,Fbefore 9am on Thursday.
OL,16,FSWR warned that services across its
OL,17,Fentire network "may be cancelled,
OL,18,Fdelayed by up to 90 minutes or
OL,19,Frevised".
OL,26,@yD@POU{D@HO]
