OL,3,CTrain passengers warned of 'major
OL,4,Cdisruption' for rest of day amid radio
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,FIt went on: "Our operations and
OL,8,Fengineering teams are working with
OL,9,Fsignallers to find and fix the fault.
OL,11,F"We do not have an ETA (estimated time
OL,12,Fof arrival) yet for when signalling
OL,13,Fwill be back to normal."
OL,15,FThe operator advised passengers to
OL,16,Fconsider using buses "while the fault
OL,17,Fis being investigated".
